OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FThis was in line with the ITA policy to
OL,7,Ftry to increase the number of
OL,8,Fcompanies.
OL,10,FFor the same reason Border and Westward
OL,11,Fcame on the air. There were legitimate
OL,12,Farguments that their transmitters could
OL,13,Fhave been allocated to neighbouring
OL,14,Festablished companies.
