OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FAnd this was one reason why the doomed
OL,7,FTeledu Cymru came into being too. It
OL,8,Fproved unviable for multiple reasons,
OL,9,Fpaving the way for a takeover by TWW
OL,10,Fand the West and Wales dual region
OL,11,Fwhich officially existed until a decade
OL,12,Fago.
OL,14,FGrampian was a different story.
OL,16,FAfter a shaky start, it soon proved
OL,17,Fhugely popular in its heartland areas
OL,18,Fand was profitable.
