OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FGrampian was one of the ITA's golden
OL,7,Fboys. A much-loved local service
OL,8,Fperfectly in tune with its core
OL,9,Faudience.
OL,11,FSTV in the 60s was anything but the
OL,12,Fgolden boy.
OL,14,FSome of its local output was personally
OL,15,Fderided by the ITA chairman Lord Hill.
OL,16,FAnd while hugely popular with the
OL,17,Fpublic, within creative circles in
OL,18,FScotland it was not uncommon to think
OL,19,FSTV could do much better.
