OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt would have been unthinkable in the
OL,7,F1967 franchise round for fundamental
OL,8,Fchanges which would simply have put
OL,9,FGrampian out of business. There was
OL,10,Fsimply no appetite for a franchise
OL,11,Fcovering central and northern Scotland.
OL,13,FInterestingly nobody competed against
OL,14,FGrampian for the licence.
OL,16,FBy then, the Angus transmitter had
OL,17,Fturned Dundee and Perth from an STV
OL,18,Ffringe into a Grampian heartland.
