OL,3,GOPINIONCThe final weeks of the remnants
OL,4,Cof Grampian TV
OL,5,
OL,6,FBy 1980, STV had improved markedly even
OL,7,Fif it still had critics. Meanwhile
OL,8,FGrampian was seen as one of the most
OL,9,Fambitious of the small companies. So
OL,10,Fthe idea of merging the two licences
OL,11,Fnever came up.
OL,13,FThe 1991 auction was based on the
OL,14,Fexisting regional structure across the
OL,15,FUK.
